<translate>
====Direct links from external sites==== <!--T:245-->
</translate>
<translate><!--T:246--> Another possibility is to use the <tvar name=1>[[Special:Redirect/file]]</tvar> page (or its alias <tvar name=2>[[Special:Filepath]]</tvar>).</translate>
<translate><!--T:247--> Unlike the above example, you can link to it from external websites as well as from MediaWiki pages.</translate>

