<translate>
====Obtaining the full URL of an image==== <!--T:249-->

<!--T:250-->
To obtain the full path of an image (without going through redirects as shown above), some <tvar name=1>{{ll|Help:magic words|nsp=0}}</tvar> can be used.
</translate>

 <nowiki>{{filepath:MediaWiki-2020-logo.svg}}</nowiki>

